            "Child-Only Driver Restriction (자녀 한정 특약): Restrict drivers to family members only for 5–10% savings. Adding young drivers (under 26) increases premiums significantly.",
            "Online Purchase Discount: 3–5% additional discount for purchasing through the insurer's website or app versus phone.",
            "Multi-year Safe Driver: 3+ years without claims? You qualify for the best discount tier, saving up to 60% off base premium through the merit rating system.",
