            "URL (HTTP/HTTPS): https?:\\/\\/(www\\.)?[a-zA-Z0-9@:%._+~#=\\-]{1,256}\\.[a-zA-Z0-9()]{1,6}\\b([a-zA-Z0-9()@:%_+.~#?&\\/=]*) — Matches most web URLs including paths and query strings.",
